CS:GO-style pack opening: decelerating roll reel that lands on your card

Replaces the instant reveal with a horizontal reel of card tiles that scrolls fast
and eases to a stop (Quint-out, ~4.6s) under a center ticker, landing on the
rarest card in the pull (with slight jitter so it isn't always dead-centre). After
it lands, the full pull fans out below, with confetti for Legendary/Mythic.

